  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/82c353361582ff2fb94071a811a8bfd3.avif?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">When children enter this mysterious park at midnight, there’s only one option: <strong>survive</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Nightshift Survival is a challenging rogue-lite game where you will face hordes of terrifying and relentless creatures in Millennium Park. What mysteries and dangers does this place hide?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/12187dbe181ce3920ba6a8d45933e7f3.poster.avif?t=1770764120\" width=616 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/12187dbe181ce3920ba6a8d45933e7f3.webm?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/12187dbe181ce3920ba6a8d45933e7f3.mp4?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Face enemies with various movement patterns, collect powerups to survive, and unlock achievements with new items and ways to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/52f5519ff2f8d98d2d20da917b4cec68.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Be a pacifist survivor or a hunter of the mysterious creatures with the 57 items, including weapons, trinkets, and collectibles available to build your best strategy to survive the insane nights.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/2346c6564f48737828be95014ab28645.poster.avif?t=1770764120\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/2346c6564f48737828be95014ab28645.webm?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/2346c6564f48737828be95014ab28645.mp4?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/7daa7e211f99d3f6c7deaef0c79b327a.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">There are 13 sinister enemies, ranging from harmless little toys to child-devouring mechatronic beasts, all eager to play with you. Face your fears through the nights to make it unscathed until 6AM and confront the bosses of each night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/845550c23cef1a21af1b3a2cff26ee87.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">With 60 achievements, unlock new possibilities to make each playthrough unique and showcase your skills as a true collector.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/366bb2554cf081f3fdc630a94b9f0572.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Play and replay with different combinations of items to take down enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Besides everything already present in the game, get ready for planned new content. Many secrets will still be revealed in the upcoming chapters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Survive the night shift, if you can.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/82c353361582ff2fb94071a811a8bfd3.avif?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">When children enter this mysterious park at midnight, there’s only one option: <strong>survive</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Nightshift Survival is a challenging rogue-lite game where you will face hordes of terrifying and relentless creatures in Millennium Park. What mysteries and dangers does this place hide?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/12187dbe181ce3920ba6a8d45933e7f3.poster.avif?t=1770764120\" width=616 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/12187dbe181ce3920ba6a8d45933e7f3.webm?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/12187dbe181ce3920ba6a8d45933e7f3.mp4?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Face enemies with various movement patterns, collect powerups to survive, and unlock achievements with new items and ways to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/52f5519ff2f8d98d2d20da917b4cec68.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Be a pacifist survivor or a hunter of the mysterious creatures with the 57 items, including weapons, trinkets, and collectibles available to build your best strategy to survive the insane nights.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/2346c6564f48737828be95014ab28645.poster.avif?t=1770764120\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/2346c6564f48737828be95014ab28645.webm?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/2346c6564f48737828be95014ab28645.mp4?t=1770764120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/7daa7e211f99d3f6c7deaef0c79b327a.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">There are 13 sinister enemies, ranging from harmless little toys to child-devouring mechatronic beasts, all eager to play with you. Face your fears through the nights to make it unscathed until 6AM and confront the bosses of each night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/845550c23cef1a21af1b3a2cff26ee87.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">With 60 achievements, unlock new possibilities to make each playthrough unique and showcase your skills as a true collector.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/366bb2554cf081f3fdc630a94b9f0572.webp?t=1770764120\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Play and replay with different combinations of items to take down enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Besides everything already present in the game, get ready for planned new content. Many secrets will still be revealed in the upcoming chapters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Survive the night shift, if you can.</strong></p>",
